\bigl(f^{-1}\bigr)'(y)={1\over f'\bigl(f^{-1}(y)\bigr)}\ .
{\rm arsinh}'(y)={1\over\cosh\bigl({\rm arsinh}(y)\bigr)}={1\over\sqrt{y^2+1}}\ \qquad(-\infty<y<\infty)
